She impressed producers after singing Katy Perry's 'Unconditionally' and Emeli Sande's 'Read all about it'.

'They said yes straight away - I couldn't believe it,' she said.

'Then they asked me what I do for a living, I think they thought I was a student or worked in a clothes shop or something.

'They were a bit surprised when I said I'm a director of an undertakers.'

